<h3><span><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4629">SCP-4629</a> &#8212; A Little Easter Egg.</strong></span></h3>
<h4><span><strong>Rating: +51</strong></span></h4>
<h4><span><strong>Genre:</strong> Comedy/Weirdness</span></h4>
<h4><span><span style="color: #66b073">So, one of us, Fred I think, did it for a minute and then boom. The sheep is in pieces and the poor guy stands there covered in blood from head to toe. Others started screaming and running away, but I personally thought the whole thing was fucking hilarious.</span></span></h4>
