<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;About&nbsp;my&nbsp;SCPs&nbsp;that&nbsp;aren't&nbsp;up&nbsp;there&nbsp;anymore</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
